    "description_long": "This is a rectangular speed limit sign displaying 'SPEED LIMIT 40' in bold black letters and numerals on a white background. The sign face is bordered by a thin black outline, giving it a clear and official appearance. It is mounted on a single, tall, rectangular post that appears to be made of metal and painted black. The back of the sign is plain and unmarked, while the post extends vertically beneath the sign face. The overall construction is sturdy and weather-resistant, suitable for outdoor urban environments. The sign is designed to be highly visible to drivers and pedestrians, ensuring compliance with local speed regulations.",
